<br>
Anika,<br>
<br>
Okay, I responded earlier while in-game with a very simple request as to whether you were going to stick by your rule #6? <br>
<br>
Are you going to ban people who make death threats and threats of physical violence? The rule says YES. If you have changed your mind just let me know because I will be up front right now that Ezboard does have a vested legal interest in making sure that it's webspace is policed against those types of threats. <br>
<br>
BTW sir, any attempt to characterize me even partially at fault here is completely without factual merit. I am no more at fault with respect to &quot;personal attacks&quot; than countless others in the Rants and Flames section of VCC. You ban me for my opinions or the manner in which I have expressed them, you'd have to ban at least a dozen others for the same reasons. My opinions simply tend to be unpopular and not embraced by the maintstream and predominately younger crowd. <br>
<br>
You appear to have missed the part in the thread in question where I warned Tendalus about moving towards the direction of making a violent threat. He and I used to be guildmates and he had made a threat of violence before on that guild's website. I tried to ameliorate the situation. <br>
<br>
Moreover, look at the thread &quot;Words of Wisdom.&quot; Emboldened by Tendalus' evidently getting just a slap on the wrist, other people have made admittedly lesser threats of physical violence. Can you see the pattern? Failure to enforce your own rule has brought about more of the behavior OR are you going to maintain that those people somehow have some reason to say what they have? <br>
<br>
Do you want a community where &quot;lines are crossed&quot; like that? Do you? How do you think my family feels? They perceive this community as &quot;anything goes&quot; where if you are in the group whose ideas have the most support you can do ANYTHING against those that you don't agree with. <br>
<br>
The community needs to know the status of rule #6. It deserves an unequivocal response.....<br>
<br>
Goanad  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/udariathvaz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dariath Vaz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Lurker</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(8/24/02 1:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm24.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: What a total bunch or retards.</span><hr size=1> Nads, you do realize you brought this upon yourself, correct?<br>
